{"tid":1920923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"發現開始有人玩割蓆","createTime":"2020-03-11T18:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T14:15:27.000Z","uid":21141,"like":99,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"de760d926344046a54cbf48b84999839f6d3eb69","tid":1920923,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T18:50:35.000Z","msg":"留意到近幾日不斷有啲人強調自己係本土派唔想再同黃絲兩個字有掛勾。我諗係時候又要提醒返大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUW6ZCh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUW6ZCh.jpg&h=108ebd41&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4XyhmQC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4XyhmQC.png&h=7c064096&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8HqvJX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8HqvJX.png&h=11d8b4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Jm3hoY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Jm3hoY.jpg&h=e8434470&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hKtJhoZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhKtJhoZ.jpg&h=26d915d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6ZXmQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6ZXmQE.jpg&h=7f25a21d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/viJk330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FviJk330.jpg&h=76614421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知好多本土派唔滿意，但希望大敵當前忍讓一下，係重要關頭能屈能伸，雖然政治理念唔同，但係大家既敵人依然係一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n梁天琦獄中公開信：真正公義還未來臨　莫被仇恨支配<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yXZcVb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyXZcVb5.png&h=2b5b54bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"43b6c02c65c894aa294e246195a069b45faea45a","tid":1920923,"uid":99725,"like":8,"dislike":36,"scor